title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Nov 11 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Nov 11 2021
description:
C&B welcome to the show, Morgan Ortagus, financial analyst and political advisor who served as spokesperson for the State Department from 2019 to 2021, unpacks the discredited Steele dossier and her dustup with Adam Schiff on The View. We're entering the world of the forever covid booster. Can Clay handle all three Travis boys this weekend? The video shows that Kyle Rittenhouse acted in self-defense. Coronabros will never admit they were wrong.
